.TH "pvrdma_modify_qp" 9 "pvrdma_modify_qp" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
pvrdma_modify_qp \- modify queue pair attributes
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" pvrdma_modify_qp
.BI "(struct ib_qp *ibqp "  ","
.BI "struct ib_qp_attr *attr "  ","
.BI "int attr_mask "  ","
.BI "struct ib_udata *udata "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "ibqp" 12
the queue pair
.IP "attr" 12
the new queue pair's attributes
.IP "attr_mask" 12
attributes mask
.IP "udata" 12
user data
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
\fIreturns\fP 0 on success, otherwise returns an errno.
